      "contents": "Lemma transport_Fc_to_idtoiso\n        s' d' u\n  : @transport _ (fun m => morphism _ (Fm m s') d') _ _ p u\n    = u o components_of (Category.Morphisms.idtoiso (_ -> _) (ap Fm p) : morphism _ _ _)^-1 s'.",
